Comment: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:48.17,Ignore,,0,0,0,,My dear Cat, good bye.\NThanks for everything you've done for me.\NI'll be watching over you for as long as I live. ⭐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:10.38,SongE,,0,0,0,,Let's take a road that goes on forever, across the hills {丘を越えどこまでも続く道　行こうみんなで}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:16.26,SongE,,0,0,0,,The blue of the sky, the green\N of the mountains, make my heart flutter  {空の青　山の緑　胸おどるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:23.95,SongE,,0,0,0,,Let's be dear friends forever,\N from the bottoms of our hearts  {心から大切な友達でいよう　いつまでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:31.32,SongE,,0,0,0,,I want to tell you with honest feelings {素直な気持ちで伝えたくて}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:37.55,SongE,,0,0,0,,No matter how lonely the night gets {たとえどんな淋しい夜が来たって}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:44.71,SongE,,0,0,0,,If you've got a friend always beside you {友達がいる　いつもすぐそばに}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:51.52,SongE,,0,0,0,,No matter how heartbreaking your love feels {たとえどんな切ない恋をしたって}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:58.68,SongE,,0,0,0,,As long as your friend is with you, \Nyou'll be all right {友達がいる　だから大丈夫}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:06.32,SongE,,0,0,0,,Let's take a road that goes on forever, across the hills {丘を越えどこまでも続く道　行こうみんなで}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:12.90,SongE,,0,0,0,,The sound of the ever-blowing wind \Nis the melody of love{流れてく風の音は恋のメロディ}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat and Star. {/Neko-kun and Hoshi-kun}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.99,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,On starry nights, Cat liked to spend time\N sitting on his favorite roof {lit, tho idk how that works if that's the only roof around and it's his own house}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.92,0:02:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and just mumble something silly, like "The stars are so beautiful."
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.30,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Star?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.54,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Star got hurt during his fall \Nand could no longer return to the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Star, why don't you come live with me\N until your injury heals?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I love the stars!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.96,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The two were always together after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:51.83,SongE,,0,0,0,,Round petals blooming in the rain {雨に咲いていた つぶらな花びら\N恋の予感に揺れて 虹色に染まるの\Nあの日の二人は 言葉で言えずに\N街角で立ち止まり 雨の音聞いてた}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.01,SongE,,0,0,0,,Swaying with a premonition of love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:04:00.44,SongE,,0,0,0,,They're dyed in rainbow colors
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:04.35,SongE,,0,0,0,,That day, the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:07.16,SongE,,0,0,0,,Couldn't express it in words
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.62,SongE,,0,0,0,,I stopped on a street corner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:15.98,SongE,,0,0,0,,And listened to the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:23.78,SongE,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I can't forget this strange melody {なぜだか 忘れられない 不思議なメロディー\N今でも 心によみがえる 思い出}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:32.87,SongE,,0,0,0,,And the memories still come to mind even to this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.53,SongE,,0,0,0,,I gradually grew to like you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:40.88,SongE,,0,0,0,,And eventually I fell in love {だんだん好きになって\Nそして だんだん恋になる\N振り向けば 足音だけが鳴ってた}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:48.26,SongE,,0,0,0,,But when I turned around,\N all I could hear were footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:56.15,SongE,,0,0,0,,Oh, good-bye to sorrow,\Nand here's to being loved {Oh 悲しみに good-bye\Nそして 愛されて乾杯\Nいつの日か また会える日を 待ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:04.20,SongE,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for the day when I can see you again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.03,SongE,,0,0,0,,Rain lingers {割れた地面に 雨が残るよ\N揺れる思いを 唄にして}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:12.50,SongE,,0,0,0,,On the cracked ground
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:20.36,SongE,,0,0,0,,Sing your swaying thoughts as a song
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.15,SongE,,0,0,0,,I gradually grew to like you {だんだん好きになって\Nそして だんだん恋になる\N何もかも 忘れられなくなってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:27.42,SongE,,0,0,0,,And eventually I fell in love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:34.94,SongE,,0,0,0,,So now I can no longer forget anything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:38.82,SongE,,0,0,0,,Oh, leave it to the wind, lonesome {Oh 風まかせ lonesome\Nいたずらな 瞳の handsome\Nすぐ そこに 時間を超えて I Love You}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:42.92,SongE,,0,0,0,,Handsome with naughty eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:47.55,SongE,,0,0,0,,Right there, beyond time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:54.30,SongE,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Star!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.98,0:06:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It's just that for some reason...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.79,0:06:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But from that day on, \NStar kept losing his vigor.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That got Cat thinking too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.81,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"What could I do to make Star cheerful again?"
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Star, look at what funny things I can do!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, whaddya think? Wasn't that funny?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it delicious, Star?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Star, look at what a funny face I can make.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Did you like it? Wasn't it funny?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.64,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Star still couldn't\N regain his liveliness.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.82,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one night, Cat finally understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.76,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Star belonged in the sky\N more than anywhere else.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.27,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Star, you should return to the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.56,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If he said that, Star would return\N to the sky with an easy heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat understood full well.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You should return...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.84,0:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After practicing countless times,\N Cat finally decided to say it today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he invited Star for a walk.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As they were walking past the house with a red roof,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat was just about to say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, it was the house with a blue roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And so Cat decided to say it there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.38,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat couldn't help feeling completely powerless when it was time to say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But once they reached\N the green-roofed house,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd say it for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Star.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.48,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that roof is more dark green than just green?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.70,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat had never been to the sky himself.{maybe "sky world" starts making more sense from here on}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.96,0:09:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was so high up,\N Cat couldn't possibly reach it on foot.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If Star returned to a place so distant,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.72,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't be able to play,\Neat dinner together,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or say hello to each other ever again.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.57,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Cat found himself\N unable to tell Star to go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Star.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.94,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Star.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Star!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Cat, goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything you've done for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.95,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be watching over you\N for as long as I live.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Star...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat cried.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.94,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was saddened to see\N Star leave, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But even more, he was mad at himself\N for not finding the strength
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to let Star go at such an important time. {lit: not being kind to star - not sure what she means}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Star was far away now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.86,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Cat knew that his friend Star\N would always be right by his side.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Star would keep sending him playful little signals. {not sure what she means: Because Hoshi-kun left a nice little mark for him - prolly cat whiskers on the star}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.38,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandit Cat's Clumsiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.60,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat sometimes goes to the town for shopping.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's always cheerful on his way back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.34,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat's favorite route is the rooftops\N of the market district. {nc what's zaito here, lit is "roofs lined up with zai"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When one day...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You could tell at a glance\N that he was a bandit,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as evident by the scars\N covering his face.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So how long are you gonna dawdle here? {unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.58,0:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he looked scary, \Nthat Bandit Cat was a little clumsy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.28,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So Cat felt like he couldn't\N just leave him there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Again?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I'm a big klutz. {unchi = 運痴 = having slow reflexes; bad at sports; unathletic person}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Claus? {unchi = うんち = poop}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the name. {/not poop}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It means my reflexes are dull. {pretty literal}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.79,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dull reflexes, you say? {lit: poop of moving, right?, or maybe not, I have no clue anymore what unchi he means here}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.26,0:12:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a really ungainly cat all my life,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,failing at even simple tasks\N ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept falling from roofs, trees, and bridges. {/falling into the river}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, my face was covered with scars, as you can see now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.89,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're not actually a bandit?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.54,0:12:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone found out that I'm such a klutz,\N everyone would make fun of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.69,0:12:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I assumed a bandit's reputation instead!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's also why I can't make any friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.41,0:13:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cat, you were lucky not to be born a clumsy cat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.19,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So please have fun in this life \Non my behalf too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.80,0:13:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is a very severe case of klutz," thought Cat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Isn't there something I could do?"
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.70,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat's forest friends gathered\N when he called them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.68,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They began a big special training regimen\N to enhance Bandit Cat's agility.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.31,0:13:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{not sure what to put, pretty much just one, two, go!}One, two, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't swim! I'm a cat! {guess in the second part}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.57,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Hey! Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.66,0:15:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! {/One, two}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.64,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he was trying his best, \NBandit Cat couldn't get any better.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.54,0:15:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandit Cat was once again shocked\Nat his own clumsiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandit Cat, your break is over.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do one last round.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.89,0:15:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit. My clumsiness is incurable.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.11,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up just yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We have to finish this training.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, gimme a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.98,0:15:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I was little, I also couldn't climb the trees for toffee.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here. I'm still climbing poorly.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone needs to practice to get good.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.65,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But me... I just... I just...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.22,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, everyone. \NLet's hop toward the settling sun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Encouraged by Cat and his friends,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.24,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandit Cat also started hopping\N determinedly up the hill.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.17,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going, keep going, \NBandit Cat! {actually just a general exclamation meaning "stay strong/go forward"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.85,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going, keep going, \NBandit Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going, keep going, \NBandit Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going, keep going, \NBandit Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Bandit Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.13,0:17:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! {g}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.82,0:17:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.19,0:17:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he was covered in sweat,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.47,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandit Cat felt that it was\N really a pleasant sweat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.01,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, Bandit Cat's\N clumsiness was cured.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Cat himself didn't notice\N when it happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was happy all the same\N that lonesome Bandit Cat
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,had finally managed to make some friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Night of the Full Moon.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.58,0:18:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Though playtime was over,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone wanted a little\N more time together.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.82,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Cat and his friends were gazing mindlessly at the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems to me that the sky's color \Nchanges all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.76,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Sun itself changes to let\N the Moon take its place, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.88,0:18:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.75,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a saying among us rabbits\N that we actually came from the Moon.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That would've been funny for sure, Rabbit!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.88,0:18:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just fairy tale stuff, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a lie.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding, nothing else.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodnight.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.63,0:19:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Rabbit...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it was just a bad joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.59,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone felt that their reaction had hurt Rabbit in some way.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.87,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Later that evening, after eating\N his dinner and taking a bath,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat thought about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.44,0:19:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a saying among us rabbits \Nthat we came from the Moon.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat thought to himself...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.01,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Back then, we laughed at Rabbit's story.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.34,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, where did I come from, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.39,0:19:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My body appeared from inside Mama when I was born.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.10,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel like my soul came\N from a whole other place.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I've become friends with Star,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit relieved\N whenever I see the Moon.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.02,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because my soul came from somewhere up in the sky?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.49,0:20:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In my dreams, I go to places\N I've never seen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be some reason\N for these dreams,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,where I'm soaring through the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because when I dream,\N my soul becomes truly free
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and is able to travel on its own, \Nwherever it wants."
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat! Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbit!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.34,0:21:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat! Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbit!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A nice place.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A nice place?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Moon!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.38,0:22:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbit's soul is also free,\N so he's able to travel to the Moon itself!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbit!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbit!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize to Rabbit
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.72,0:22:21.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,for bursting into laughter\N without a second thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.32,0:22:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Restless, Cat soon found himself out on the road
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.41,0:22:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and was already approaching\N Rabbit's house.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.38,0:22:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.89,0:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear! Squirrel!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.25,0:22:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Raccoon!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.24,0:22:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbit!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.43,0:23:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.05,0:23:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.89,0:23:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.35,0:23:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive us, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.93,0:23:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you believe me now! {guess, yokatta ne?}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.13,0:23:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Rabbit told Cat plenty of stories about the Moon.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.82,0:23:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Cat ended up liking\N the Moon more than ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.54,0:23:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's Rabbit!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.43,0:24:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Flying Blanket.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.31,0:24:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened one warm and really pleasant morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:29.91,0:24:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat decided to hang\N his blanket out to dry.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:35.85,0:24:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought it'd be nice if his blanket smelled of sun in the evening,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.00,0:24:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat got to work on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:43.00,0:24:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Warmed by gentle sun,\N his blanket became nice and fluffy.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.34,0:24:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great feeling!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.00,0:24:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat couldn't wait until night
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.19,0:24:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and was soon napping peacefully.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:54.91,0:24:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then suddenly...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.89,0:25:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:34.25,0:25:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:39.01,0:25:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.24,0:25:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:46.24,0:25:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.56,0:25:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going? {/I'm going}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:49.56,0:25:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:05.92,0:27:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:19.33,0:27:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Crows!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:31.92,0:27:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:38.39,0:27:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop! {/Hey}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:03.23,0:28:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:19.76,0:28:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.68,0:28:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The rainbow he was cheerfully admiring
Dialogue: 10,0:28:39.13,0:28:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was so beautiful \Nit took Cat's breath away.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:53.01,0:28:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was gradually getting dark,\Nand Cat started to feel very lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:00.43,0:29:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's turn back already.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:02.65,0:29:05.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,Who knows how far this blanket will fly?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.63,0:29:07.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:07.85,0:29:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then suddenly...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:09.87,0:29:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Star noticed Cat, who was in a pickle.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:13.00,0:29:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat needs my help!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.58,0:29:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way Star would leave Cat, who had shared
Dialogue: 10,0:29:20.21,0:29:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a meal with him, \Nto fend for himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:22.05,0:29:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:23.14,0:29:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:25.52,0:29:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Star!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:31.04,0:29:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,By steering his blanket\N with the air escaping from it,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:34.15,0:29:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat managed to return home safely.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:38.65,0:29:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Star!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:40.95,0:29:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever need anything, \NI'm always here to help! {unsure, he/she kinda mumbles words}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.97,0:29:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I come to play,\N even when I don't need anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:47.75,0:29:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:50.76,0:29:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Star returned to the sky once more.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.94,0:29:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, neither of them shed a tear.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.35,0:30:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, no matter how far away your friend is,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:02.30,0:30:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll remain friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.01,0:30:31.88,SongE,,0,0,0,,When I look at the night sky {no lyrics, going by ear}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.88,0:30:36.84,SongE,,0,0,0,,Your warmth flows
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.84,0:30:46.32,SongE,,0,0,0,,Along with the quiet breeze, it's wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.64,0:30:56.46,SongE,,0,0,0,,Wrapped in this gentle light
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.46,0:31:05.09,SongE,,0,0,0,,I can't help thinking of the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.55,0:31:16.16,SongE,,0,0,0,,We all have moments\N when our hearts tremble and feel lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.16,0:31:25.94,SongE,,0,0,0,,But let those tears fly away to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.27,0:31:30.29,SongE,,0,0,0,,My tiny little dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.20,0:31:36.16,SongE,,0,0,0,,I won't let it grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.16,0:31:40.31,SongE,,0,0,0,,I may be tired
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.98,0:31:45.58,SongE,,0,0,0,,But I won't get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.58,0:31:52.39,SongE,,0,0,0,,Someone out there loves you
